they actually practiced by
getting every big decision

00:14:04.396 --> 00:14:05.520
maker in the room together.

00:14:05.520 --> 00:14:09.060
So they got the legal team, the
executives, the social media,

00:14:09.060 --> 00:14:13.130
the design agency to come
together for every big event

00:14:13.130 --> 00:14:16.540
